Text.string: We got a heavy over here!
I knew I had it in me.
Ura! (Russian battle cry, not to be confused with US Marines "oorah").
B-B-B-BYYEOOWW (my best attempt at rendering airhorn in text)
Sarge is gonna kill me for this…
Guess you're not as special as you thought!
Say buongiorno to my tiny amigo!
Nobody breaks my bear and gets away with it!
You think I need Iron Cub to kill you?
Whoever killed my cub is DEAD!
You killed the cub! BLOOD FEEEUUUUD!
Aw, man! Now I have to kill you all by myself!
The ol' exploding mini bear mech trick! Gets 'em every time.
You were too good for this world anyway!
The cub'll come back. You won't.
Aw, come on cub, stick around!
Fine, be that way, I'll just kick ass on my own!
Hurry up and refuel, we got asses to kick!
Don't worry Iron Cub, mama's got this!
Cub's empty! Guess it's up to me…
Aw, but we were just getting started!
The party's over already? Come oooon…
No no no, you can't do this to me!
Dammit, cub, we've got work to do!
I can do this all day!
Man, this sucks. At least sitting around in Iron Bear, I've got a comfy seat. I hate standing…
I should text Amara. Get brunch sometime… a few mimosas…
Don't lock your knees, don't lock your knees, don't lock your knees…
Lead and iron by the ton, / No one's got a bigger gun / Don't need rifles, don't need ranks / When you've got a walking tank.
Rockets, bullets, fists, and frags / Vladof army's got the mags / If you miss in Ursa Corps / Shoot and shoot and shoot some more.
